    "title": "Easyday is Hiring: Floor Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Easyday! We are hiring a Floor Manager for our Agra team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Easyday:\nEasyday is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Handle customer queries, complaints, and escalations effectively\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Prepare daily sales reports and share insights with management\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Ensure compliance with company policies and retail regulations\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in CRM\n• Proficiency in KPI Management\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Shrinkage Control\n• Proficiency in Retail Operations\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Easyday!",
